txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Needed: Large filth from the insects and spiders plaguing Meluinen. Deliver the items to Thaliollang at Lin Giliath.
'I will begin studying this immediately. Thank you for your efforts.'
'I wish to study the filth covering the insects and spiders within Meluinen.'
Elves of Rivendell Task: Large Filth
Thaliollang in the Elf-ruin of Meluinen at Lin Giliath requires the return of large filth.
Deliver the large filth to Thaliollang at Lin Giliath
You are on a task to collect large filth from the insects and spiders plaguing Meluinen and to deliver them to Thaliollang. Thaliollang can be found at Lin Giliath, the Elf-ruins of Meluinen.
Needed: Large filth from the insects and spiders plaguing Meluinen.
